Modifications by Coder4 (2026):

  * Renamed package metadata and entry points to anycontent-vault-backend.
  * Added URL routing in web/app.py to dispatch to platform-specific extractors
    based on the source URL (Douyin / TikTok / WeChat / YouTube).
  * Added web/wechat_extractor.py for WeChat Official Account article scraping
    (BeautifulSoup-based, mobile UA, inline image references).
  * Added web/youtube_extractor.py for YouTube transcript + metadata fetching
    (oEmbed + youtube-transcript-api).
  * Extended ExtractResponse to carry platform, post_type, author, account,
    publish_time, thumbnail, and images_markdown fields.
  * Modified douyin-video/scripts/douyin_downloader.py:
      - Detect image-post (note) URLs (/share/note/, aweme_type=2) and route
        them through the OCR pipeline.
      - Add a fallback chain across SiliconFlow VL models (Qwen3-VL series).
      - Validate API key encoding to surface helpful errors for non-ASCII input.

